### TaskBoard API Sample Requests
### Save this file as sample-requests.http in VS Code with REST Client extension

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000
@contentType = application/json

### Create a new task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Complete API Documentation",
  "description": "Write comprehensive documentation for the TaskBoard API",
  "priority": "High"
}

### Get all tasks (no filtering)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems

### Get tasks with status filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems?status=Todo

### Get tasks with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems?page=1&pageSize=5

### Get tasks with status filter and pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems?status=InProgress&page=1&pageSize=10

### Get a specific task (replace 1 with actual task ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems/1

### Update a task (replace 1 with actual task ID and RowVersion)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
If-Match: "AAAAAAAAB9s="

{
  "title": "Updated Task Title",
  "description": "This is the updated description",
  "priority": "Medium"
}

### Update task status only (replace 1 with actual task ID and RowVersion)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems/1/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
If-Match: "AAAAAAAAB9s="

{
  "status": "InProgress"
}

### Invalid status transition (should return error)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/taskitems/1/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
If-Match: "AAAAAAAAB9s="

{
  "status": "Done"
}

